data.description: This 3388 square foot single family home has 4 bedrooms and 4.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 3434 Triple Crown St, Celina, TX 75009.
data.whatILove:
This 1.5 story home is full of designer style! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac and sitting above the home directly behind it, the backyard of this lot has privacy on all sides. Upgrades include:

-Exterior uplighting
-Brick style
-Mud room built-ins
-8 foot doorways
-Level 7 hardwood floors
-Hardwired for speakers
-Undercabinet lighting in kitchen and pocket office
-Pocket office (in addition to study), is complete with built-ins
-Extended patio areas in backyard
-Fully landscaped front and back yard


Some additional features in the home include vaulted ceilings in 3 of the 4 bedrooms, game room and bathroom upstairs, 12 foot ceilings in entryway, huge master bath complete with step down oversized shower, large closet, modern shaker style cabinets with upgraded hardware, modern fireplace and all new fans and light fixtures. With a media room centrally located on the main floor, it's the perfect location for hosting football parties that everyone can enjoy together.
